snippet.title: Five Nights at Raiden's | 1.2 Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for update 1.2 for Five Nights at Raiden's!
In update you will see...
- Hard Mode, that will unlock after 5 Main Nights!
- Reworked Sprites!
- Over 25 new tracks!
- Full Russian Localization!
- 3 New Gamemodes
- Extra Options for Post-Mission!
- HellFire Challenge!
- 10 New Skins!
- 31 Achievement!
- And More-more!
You can download game on Itch.io and GameJolt!
Itch.Io: https://lolhaker.itch.io/genshin-impact-five-nights-at-raidens
GameJolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/GI_FNAR/797064
